   198â†’
   199â†’## TYPESCRIPT QUALITY RULES
   200â†’
   201â†’### Type Safety Rules
   202â†’- **Strict TypeScript**: Always use strict mode
   203â†’- **No any types**: Use proper interfaces and union types
   204â†’- **Explicit return types**: For all public functions
   205â†’- **Null safety**: Handle undefined/null cases explicitly
   206â†’
   207â†’### Function Rules
